descript.abstract: HUC-8 coverage for the Chespaeake Bay watershed states--referred to here as the Mid-Atlantic states--level was created by dissolving huc11_hr02.
descript.purpose: Originally compiled for Chesapeake Bay Program mapping and analysis.
descript.supplinf: HUC-11 boundaries are compiled by each state. The export files of HUC-11 at the state level were provided by each respective state and are unmodified. HUC-11 boundaries for Delaware are not yet available. Also, a small portion of the Chesapeake Basin in NY State has not yet been completed.

idinfo.native: Microsoft Windows 2000 Version 5.2 (Build 3790) Service Pack 2; ESRI ArcCatalog 9.3.1.1850

dataqual.complete: HUC-11 boundaries for Delaware are not yet available. Also, a small portion of the Chesapeake Bay Basin in NY State that does not yet have officially designated HUC-11 boundaries has been 'filled-in' with watershed boundaries by delineating and digitizing them from 1:24,000 scaled USGS topographic maps of the area by the Chesapeake Bay Program GIS Team.
